M7 Priest Tank is the second tank I've ever made on hammer editor. It's been a while since I worked on it. So I present to you the Beta of this version. 

 Functions:

 -Turret shoots
 -Sounds included
 -Moves on path tracks


  This is the beta. I plan on releasing the final once I master physic_box :)

-You credit me if you use this
-You are not allowed to use plagiarism (re-release this and take credit for yourself)
